<h1>Welcome to Quadruple Square</h1>
<h2>Game Rules</h2>
<p>The game consists of capturing as many cards as possible from the game board.</p>
<p>To capture a card, drag and drop it onto an empty slot. The adjacent card's power must be lower than the power of the card placed on that side.</p>
<p>Once the game board is full, the player with the most captured cards wins.</p>
<p>First, choose five cards from your own collection by clicking on them.</p>
<p>If you make a mistake, click the card again in your selected cards to withdraw it.</p>

<p>At the end of the match, the winner gets to chose a card from the opposite player's collection.</p>